IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User jvshahid@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 --decrypt ~/.mbsyncpass.gpg" # created with gpg2 -c --output ~/.mbsyncpass.gpg ~/.mbsyncpass
Port 993
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs Login
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Maildir/gmail/
Inbox ~/Maildir/gmail/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim
AltMap yes

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/Spam"
Create Slave
MaxMessages 100
Sync All
Expunge None
ExpireUnread yes
SyncState *
